At the servlet 4.0 Implementation at javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
is a bug:

The release method not release all attibutes:

   /**
     * Release state.
     *
     * @see Tag#release()
     */

    public void release() {
	parent          = null;
    }

better is
   public void release() {
	parent          = null;
        id = null ;
        values = null ;
        pageContext = null ;
   }

I have trouble with this implementation at Tag Pooling!

    }
